{"word":"G1821 - ἐξαποστέλλω - exapostéllō - ex-ap-os-tel'-lo - Send","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαποστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exapostéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ap-os-tel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Send</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனுப்பிவிடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to send forth"},{"paragraph":"2. to send away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G649 - ἀποστέλλω - apostéllō - ap-os-tel'-lo/649\">G649</a>; to <i>send away forth</i>, that is, (on a mission) to <i>despatch</i>, or (peremptorily) to <i>dismiss:</i> - send (away, forth, out).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1821/1821\">G1821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3992/3992\">G3992</a>, <a href=\"#/G5570/5570\">G5570</a>, <a href=\"#/G649/649\">G649</a>, <a href=\"#/G651/651\">G651</a>, <a href=\"#/G652/652\">G652</a>"}]}